{% doc %}
  @prompt
    **“Create a product-grid section inspired by the layout of Forty Four Winks.
    Use rounded capsule-shaped product cards (very large border-radius ~120px).
    Each product card includes:
    – Product image
    – Product title
    – Product price
    – A small star icon under the price that instantly adds the product to cart when tapped (no redirect, no popup).
    Make the star icon minimal, thin-line, black.
    On hover (desktop), the star slightly glows.
    On click, the product is added to cart directly.
    
    GRID BEHAVIOR:
    – Desktop: 4 products per row
    – Mobile: 2 products per row 
    – Even spacing between items
    – Fade-to-white gradient at the bottom of the grid (same as reference)
    
    CARD DESIGN:
    – Background: #F5F5F5
    – Rounded shape: large, soft, capsule shape
    – Image fits inside card without touching edges
    – Text centered
    – Very minimal aesthetic
    
    STAR ADD-TO-CART FUNCTION (IMPORTANT):
    – The star icon must run JS: add the product variant to cart in the background
    – Do not redirect to cart page
    – After adding, briefly change the icon color to black for 0.2s then return to normal
    – Use fetch('/cart/add.js') method
    
    Make sure HTML, CSS, and JS are clean and inserted inside the custom liquid block automatically.
    
    Also ensure the section works whether the user is logged in or not.”**, Please update this product-grid section to match these requirements:
    
    Card shape
    – Make every product card a tall rounded rectangle (capsule), not a circle/oval around the icon.
    – The card should be clearly taller than it is wide (similar to 3:4 proportion).
    – Use a large border radius only on the corners, like border-radius: 120px;, so it looks like a rounded rectangle, not a circle.
    – Keep the card background a very light grey (#F5F5F5) and remove any visible border.
    – Center the product image, title and price vertically inside the card with lots of empty space at the top and bottom, like the reference.
    
    Star icon as Add to Cart button
    – The small star under the price must be an interactive add-to-cart button for that product.
    – When the star is clicked, add 1 of the selected / first available variant to the cart using JavaScript (fetch('/cart/add.js')) without leaving the page and without reloading.
    – After a successful add, give a small visual feedback: briefly fill the star or change its color, then return it to normal, and optionally show a short “Added to cart” message.
    – On hover (desktop), make the star slightly glow or thicken so it feels clickable.
    
    Layout
    – Keep 4 cards per row on desktop, 2 cards per row on mobile, with equal spacing between cards.
    – Keep the minimal, clean style similar to Forty Four Winks.
    
    Do not change the basic grid structure, only adjust the shapes to tall rounded rectangles and make the star a real add-to-cart button with the behavior described above., The mobile product cards are still too circular.
    Please adjust the card shape so it matches the tall rounded rectangles (capsules) from the reference:
    
    – Each product card should be clearly taller than it is wide, not a circle around the content.
    – On mobile, set the card to roughly a 3:4 proportion (for example: width about 48% of the container and a fixed min-height of about 320–360px).
    – Keep the soft corners but do not make it fully round: use a large corner radius only (for example border-radius: 80px or similar), so it looks like a tall rounded rectangle.
    – The light grey background should fill the entire capsule from top to bottom, with the image, title, price and star sitting inside it (star near the bottom, not touching the edge).
    – Keep 2 cards per row on mobile and don’t change the grid or star behavior, only the card shape and proportions.
    
    Do not change any other parts of the layout or functionality., adjust that 4 are visible in the desktop display because they need extra scrolling to the right 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}

/* Hide section on desktop */
@media (min-width: 750px) {
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} {
    display: none !important;
  }
}

/* Existing CSS below */
  .ai-product-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-product-grid-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-product-grid-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding_top }}px {{ block.settings.card_padding_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.card_padding_bottom }}px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    min-height: 400px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .ai-product-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.image_max_width }}%;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.image_spacing }}px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.image_border_radius }}px;
  }

  .ai-product-card-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-product-card-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background-color: #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.image_border_radius }}px;
  }

  .ai-product-card-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-product-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_spacing }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-product-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .ai-product-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 9px;
    color: {{ block.settings.price_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.price_spacing }}px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .ai-add-to-cart-star-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.star_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.star_size }}px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-add-to-cart-star-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    stroke: {{ block.settings.star_color }};
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: {{ block.settings.star_stroke_width }};
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-add-to-cart-star-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover svg {
    stroke-width: {{ block.settings.star_stroke_width | plus: 0.5 }};
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 {{ block.settings.star_glow_size }}px {{ block.settings.star_glow_color }});
  }

  .ai-add-to-cart-star-{{ ai_gen_id }}.adding svg {
    fill: {{ block.settings.star_color }};
    stroke: {{ block.settings.star_color }};
  }

  .ai-add-to-cart-feedback-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -25px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: {{ block.settings.feedback_color }};
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-add-to-cart-feedback-{{ ai_gen_id }}.show {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .ai-grid-fade-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: {{ block.settings.fade_height }}px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, {{ block.settings.fade_start_color }}, {{ block.settings.fade_end_color }});
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-product-grid-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_mobile }}, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding_top_mobile }}px {{ block.settings.card_padding_horizontal_mobile }}px {{ block.settings.card_padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
      border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius_mobile }}px;
      min-height: {{ block.settings.card_min_height_mobile }}px;
      aspect-ratio: auto;
    }

    .ai-product-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    .ai-product-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 9px;
    }

    .ai-add-to-cart-star-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.star_size_mobile }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.star_size_mobile }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<product-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-product-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-product-grid-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-product-grid-items-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.collection != blank %}
        {% for product in block.settings.collection.products limit: block.settings.products_limit %}
          <div class="ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="ai-product-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if product.featured_image %}
                <img
                  src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }}"
                  alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                  class="ai-product-card-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="600"
                  height="{{ 600 | divided_by: product.featured_image.aspect_ratio | round }}"
                >
              {% else %}
                <div class="ai-product-card-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            </a>
            
            <h3 class="ai-product-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <a href="{{ product.url }}">{{ product.title }}</a>
            </h3>
            
            <div class="ai-product-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ product.price | money }}
            </div>
            
            <div style="position: relative;">
              <button
                class="ai-add-to-cart-star-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
                data-variant-id="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}"
                data-product-title="{{ product.title | escape }}"
                aria-label="Add {{ product.title }} to cart"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="ai-add-to-cart-feedback-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feedback_text }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      {% else %}
        {% for i in (1..block.settings.products_limit) %}
          <div class="ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-product-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-product-card-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="ai-product-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              Product title
            </h3>
            
            <div class="ai-product-card-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              EGP 0.00
            </div>
            
            <div style="position: relative;">
              <button class="ai-add-to-cart-star-{{ ai_gen_id }}" disabled aria-label="Add to cart">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="ai-add-to-cart-feedback-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feedback_text }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    
    {% if block.settings.show_fade %}
      <div class="ai-grid-fade-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</product-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class ProductGrid{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.stars = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-add-to-cart-star-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.setupEventListeners();
      }

      setupEventListeners() {
        this.stars.forEach((star) => {
          star.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            e.stopPropagation();
            this.addToCart(star);
          });
        });
      }

      async addToCart(button) {
        const variantId = button.getAttribute('data-variant-id');
        const productTitle = button.getAttribute('data-product-title');
        
        if (!variantId || button.disabled) {
          return;
        }

        button.disabled = true;
        button.classList.add('adding');

        const feedbackElement = button.parentElement.querySelector('.ai-add-to-cart-feedback-{{ ai_gen_id }}');

        try {
          const response = await fetch('/cart/add.js', {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: {
              'Content-Type': 'application/json',
            },
            body: JSON.stringify({
              id: variantId,
              quantity: 1
            })
          });

          if (!response.ok) {
            throw new Error('Failed to add to cart');
          }

          const data = await response.json();

          if (feedbackElement) {
            feedbackElement.classList.add('show');
          }

          setTimeout(() => {
            button.classList.remove('adding');
            button.disabled = false;
            if (feedbackElement) {
              feedbackElement.classList.remove('show');
            }
          }, 1500);

          document.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('cart:updated'));

          if (window.theme && window.theme.cart) {
            window.theme.cart.refresh();
          }

          const cartDrawer = document.querySelector('cart-drawer');
          if (cartDrawer && typeof cartDrawer.renderContents === 'function') {
            fetch('/cart.js')
              .then(response => response.json())
              .then(cart => {
                cartDrawer.renderContents(cart);
              });
          }

        } catch (error) {
          console.error('Error adding to cart:', error);
          button.classList.remove('adding');
          button.disabled = false;
          
          if (feedbackElement) {
            feedbackElement.textContent = 'Error';
            feedbackElement.classList.add('show');
            setTimeout(() => {
              feedbackElement.classList.remove('show');
              feedbackElement.textContent = '{{ block.settings.feedback_text }}';
            }, 1500);
          }
        }
      }
    }

    customElements.define('product-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}', ProductGrid{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

